Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:09.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,彼得将会给你指路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Peter will point the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.16,0:00:10.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,《失落的秘符》前情提要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Previously on "The Lost Symbol"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:11.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,他抓走了彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's got Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:14.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,中情局  我以为联调局负责绑架案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}CIA? I thought the Bureau handled kidnappings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:15.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以说这只手属于彼得·所罗门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, this hand belonged to Peter Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:17.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,彼得是我的导师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Peter was my mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:18.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,所罗门的孩子为我们工作过吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Solomon's kid worked for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:20.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,很短暂  三年期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Briefly. Three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:22.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,他被殴打致死  在安卡拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was beaten to death. In Ankara.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.70,0:00:25.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,尖顶石可以完善这段信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The capstone could complete the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:28.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,迈拉克需要你去找入口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mal'akh needs you to find the portal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.91,0:00:30.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有很多工作要做  罗伯特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have more work to do, Robert.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:32.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的命运现在掌握在罗伯特的手中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your fate is in Robert's hands now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:34.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果我要帮助你爸爸  我就得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I'm gonna help your dad, I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:36.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要跟你一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm coming with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:58.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs18\frz357\b0\3a&HFF\c&H3D3C31\pos(99.6,242.133)}地铁换乘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.14,0:01:05.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,-那是什么  -镀金边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What is that? - Gilded edges,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.27,0:01:07.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,希伯来语...可能是经文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hebrew... Probably a religious text.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.35,0:01:11.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,[希伯来语]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:14.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的希伯来语有点生疏了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, my Hebrew's a little rusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.00,0:01:15.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,行了  我有个应用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, I have an app.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.79,0:01:18.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  你从来不用谷歌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right. 'Cause you never Google.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.10,0:01:20.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我可没出声  -嗯  我看得懂你的表情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I didn't say anything. - Yeah, I know your looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.02,0:01:21.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在全球意识项目中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I work on the Global Consciousness Project
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.53,0:01:22.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,与来自世界各地的科学家共事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with scientists from all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.37,0:01:24.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个应用救过我不止一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This has saved me more than once.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.16,0:01:29.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,《旧约》中的《列王纪上》  第三章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First Kings, chapter three. Old Testament.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.47,0:01:31.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,《列王纪上》  第三章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First Kings, chapter three.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.05,0:01:33.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,"所罗门王的审判"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, the Judgement of Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.10,0:01:38.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,兰登...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Langdon...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.47,0:01:42.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\fs18\b0\3a&HFF\c&HDDDEC9\frz336.5\pos(280,107.733)}把手机扔了\N他们可以追踪你们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:41.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么  这是谁发来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? Who sent this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.72,0:01:42.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs18\b0\frz336.5\3a&HFF\c&HDDDEC9\pos(313.2,147.2)}越过行者去找狼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.42,0:01:44.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,"越过行者去找狼"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Pass the wayfarer. Find the wolf."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.65,0:01:47.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:51.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:01:56.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,-凯瑟琳  -怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Katherine.  - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:01:57.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的手机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:03.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,越过行者...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pass the wayfarer...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:05.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,你干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:14.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,去找狼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Find the wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:18.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,这儿有个门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a hatch here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:33.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,右边有个插销\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a bolt to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.49,0:02:35.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,把它插上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Slide it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.56,0:02:36.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,沃伦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Warren?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:38.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你  凯瑟琳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's good to see you, Katherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:41.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉我们是在这种情况下见面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry it's under these circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:43.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,-手机  -我们丢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Phones? - We left them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:45.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,-很好  -有人想要和我解释一下吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Good. - Does someone want to tell me what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.61,0:02:47.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以边走边聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can talk on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:09.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,是在哪里跟丢的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where'd you lose him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:11.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,通往站台的隧道里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tunnel, on the way to the platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:13.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  他上一秒还在  下一秒就不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know. He was there, then he wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:15.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,所罗门的女儿和他在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Solomon's daughter was with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:16.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Katherine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:17.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们会继续找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll keep looking,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:19.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,查看摄像头  梳理轨迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}check the cameras, comb the tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:21.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,-他们一定就在附近  -老大来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- They've got to be close. - Boss is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:22.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,有情况向我汇报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep me posted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:31.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,如今我们面临着怨声载道的员工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're saying disgruntled employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:32.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,工作场所的枪击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Workplace shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:34.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,-且无关政治  -是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Apolitical. - It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:35.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,我留他一个人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I left him exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:37.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,你做了你应该做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You did your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:39.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,枪手是什么情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about the shooter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:43.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,清洁工叫尼古拉斯·巴斯庭  37岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The janitor is Nicholas Bastin. 37.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:47.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}机密信息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:46.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,前军医  2015年光荣退伍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Former Army medic. Honorable discharge 2015.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.15,0:03:48.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,无犯罪记录  政治立场不明确\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No criminal record. Politically ambivalent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,六个月前  他失踪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Six months ago, he goes off the grid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:53.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,-另一个呢  -没有线索  他就是个幽灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And the other one? - No hits. He's a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:54.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}机密信息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:55.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,除了在国会大厦留下了一只断手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And in addition to leaving a severed hand at the Capitol,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:56.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,他还在一英里外的公园\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he left two uniforms half-dead
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,把两位警察打得半死不活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in the park a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.83,0:04:02.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果这之间有联系呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if there's a connection?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:03.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,跟什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:08.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,扎克里·所罗门死于土耳其的监狱暴动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Zachary Solomon died in a prison riot in Turkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:10.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,而杀他的凶手...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And whoever killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:15.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}机密信息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:13.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,留下了这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}left this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:16.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,三曲腿图  这是共济会的重要符号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Triskelion. It's an important symbol in Freemasonry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:18.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,也许是你过度解读了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or maybe you're reading too much into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:20.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,你把它变成私人恩怨了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're making it personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:21.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:23.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在国会大厦地下室发现的手工制品呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the artifact you found in the Capitol basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:25.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,金字塔跟兰登一起消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The pyramid's gone. With Langdon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:28.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,那其中藏了很多秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And with it, many secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:30.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们听说过这个入口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've heard of this portal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:31.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们对它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we are interested in it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:33.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,以及它可能蕴含的信息很感兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and any information it might lead to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:34.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,但依我看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But from where I'm sitting,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:38.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们似乎已经错过了找到它的最佳时机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it looks like our best chance to find it has flown the coop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:40.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要兰登\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need Langdon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:42.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,那彼得·所罗门呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about Peter Solomon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:44.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以双管齐下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can walk and chew gum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:48.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我不会在这上面抱太大期望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I would manage my expectations on that front.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:50.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,彼得在阿拉弗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Peter is in the Araf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:50.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3\pos(380,235)\fs14\b0\bord0\shad0}穆斯林的炼狱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:52.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:54.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,天堂和地狱之间的分界线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The borderland between Heaven and Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.49,0:04:56.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢了  我知道阿拉弗是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, thank you. I know what the Araf is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:58.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,他是否能返回到你的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And whether he returns to your world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,亦或直奔下一程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or moves on to the next
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:02.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,取决于你此刻的行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}will depend on your actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:03.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,他可能已经死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He might already be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:06.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,那通电话是用所罗门的手机打的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That call was made from Solomon's phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:09.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在监听他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were monitoring him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:13.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们监听很多人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We monitor a great many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:20.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,找到兰登\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Find Langdon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:28.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我跟彼得当了30年朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been friends with Peter for 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:30.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,共济会会友吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Freemason friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:32.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,《回头的行者》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"The Wayfarer."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:35.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,博斯的一幅画  因涉及共济会闻名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A painting by Bosch known for its Masonic references.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:37.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉发了这么多神秘信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry for all the cryptic texts,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:39.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,我担心你的信息被监控了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I was afraid your messages were being monitored.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:40.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:42.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,那我们现在直接跟着你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we're just supposed to follow you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:43.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,-没问题  -我相信他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No questions. - I trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:44.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,他就像我和扎克的叔叔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was like an uncle to me and Zach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:46.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,这解释不了他怎么知道在哪能找到我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which doesn't explain how he knew where to find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,我以前在国务院工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I used to be with the State Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:51.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,后来我有了新工作  国会大厦建筑师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I got a new job: Architect of the Capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:52.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,国会大厦建筑群\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which puts me in charge
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:55.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,所有的建筑都由我负责\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of every building in the Capitol complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:58.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这些楼里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know everything that goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:02.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,和楼底的一切情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in these buildings and under them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:08.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在在国会图书馆的下方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're under the Library of Congress now--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:10.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,从前的流通书库\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the old circulation room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:19.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,-这是...  -以前的传输系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So that's the, uh... - The old conveyor system.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:22.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,它在另外两栋楼下传输书籍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It ran books under the other two buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:24.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们在这里很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, you'll be safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:25.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,这段时间低调行事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just lay low for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:27.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,低调行事  这对我爸有什么帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lay low? How is that going to help Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:30.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,等到我们想出下一步计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just until we figure out our next steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:38.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,我能看看吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May I see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,我用共济会密码\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I used the Mason cipher
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:02.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,破译过  但...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to translate it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:05.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,这需要尖顶石才能破译\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It requires the capstone to be understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:07.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道尖顶石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know about the capstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我们在哪能找到它吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know where we can find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:14.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:19.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,很久以前  共济会会长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Long ago, the Master Masons,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:21.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们把金字塔和尖顶石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they hid the pyramid and the capstone
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:24.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,藏在两个不同的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in two different locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:26.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,没人能同时知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one person is allowed to know
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:29.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,两者的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the location of both pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:32.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,我爸把这个藏在了保险箱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dad kept this in his safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:33.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们觉得这可能是条线索\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We think it might be a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,出自《列王记》之《所罗门的审判》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's from First Kings. The Judgment of Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:36.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,只是老套\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just your typical,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:38.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有点烦人的圣经故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}moderately disturbing Bible tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:39.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道他为什么要把这个放在保险柜里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know why he'd keep it in a safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:41.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我也不明白  -一定和某个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Neither do I. - There has to be
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:44.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们都知道的故事有关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}something about this beyond the story we all know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:48.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果是这样  我完全不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, if there is, I don't know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:53.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,休息吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:55.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,我去找人调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll press my contacts to find out
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:58.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,是否有你父亲下落的其他信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if there's more information about your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:00.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Katherine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:03.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:31.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,你还有个手机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Extra phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:36.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:42.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,之前在国会大厦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Back at the Capitol,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:46.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们把我关在一间屋子里  有警卫看守\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they had me in a room, under guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:50.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,有个打扮成清洁工的人进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A man came in dressed like a janitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:55.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,他开枪杀了警卫  然后给了我这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He shot the guards and gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:08:59.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,迈拉克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mal'akh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:02.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,他这么称呼对方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what he called him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:05.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,那个掳走彼得的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The person who took Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.49,0:09:07.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,到底有多少人和这件事有关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How many people are a part of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:09.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:10.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,还有那只手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:12.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道是我爸的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do they know it was Dad's?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:15.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,是他的戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was his ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:17.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,戒指可以调换\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, a ring can be switched.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:20.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,那只手是最近被斩断的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The hand had been severed... recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,那还是不能证明是他的手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That still doesn't prove it was his.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:23.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Y-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:24.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,别来这套\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:27.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,不要顺着我的话说  我不会崩溃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't humor me. I'm not going to break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:29.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道该怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I don't know what I'm supposed to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:31.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,意料之中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:34.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我只是在消化这所有的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. I'm just trying to process all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:42.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只是希望他能平安无事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just need him to be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:50.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:14.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur6\frz356\fs18\b0\3a&FHH\c&H161412\t(0,290,1,\blur0)\pos(236,95.467)}逮捕令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:14.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur8\frz349.6\fs12\b0\3a&FHH\c&H161412\t(0,500,1,\blur0)\pos(153.2,183.467)}扎克里·所罗门
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:15.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,贩毒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trafficking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:16.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What does that even mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:19.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs18\b0\3a&HFF\c&HFFFFFF\fad(950,920)\pos(192,230.933)}三年前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:19.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,一般来说  这是指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, u-usually, it refers to, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:21.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,非法贩卖毒品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}illegal trading, dealing narcotics...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:23.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个案子中  在扎克里家中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In this case, a staggering amount of heroin
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:24.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,发现了大量海洛因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}found in Zachary's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:26.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,问题是  我们该怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The question is, what are we going to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:28.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,萨辛教授为人权观察组织\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Professor Sahin wrote a study
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:31.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,写过一篇关于土耳其司法系统的研究\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on the Turkish justice system for Human Rights Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.05,0:11:31.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,她在那可能有认识的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She might have a contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,或许他就需要这样的经历\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe this is just what he needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:35.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,任由他烂在一个第二世界的监狱里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To rot in a decrepit, Second World prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:38.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,自己的错自己承担  不能总指望有人会救他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To not be rescued from his own mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:40.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在他需要的不是你的教训\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He doesn't need your lessons right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:41.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,他需要的是你的爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He needs your love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:43.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,我给了他我的爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I gave him my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:44.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,他拒绝了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He rejected it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:46.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想要他和你一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wanted him to be just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:50.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,像你一样沉迷于这些无关紧要的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To share in your obsession with all of this... trivia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:52.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,他拒绝的是这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what he rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:54.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,但这并不意味着你不再是他的父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it doesn't mean that you get to stop being his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.99,0:11:56.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,我先失陪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:02.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不会真的觉得我们应该把他丢在那吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't really think we should leave him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:05.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特  我这样不公平吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Robert, am I being unfair here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:07.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不必回答这个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You-you don't have to answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你只是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I think you're just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:11.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个处境艰难的父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a father in a difficult situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:14.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,我能理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I... I get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:50.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,兰登  你要干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Langdon, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.11,0:12:52.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,放开  他拿走了那页纸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let go. He took the page.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:54.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我早就觉得他之前有所隐瞒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought he was holding something back before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:56.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,他知道为什么这个很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He knows why it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:57.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:12:58.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,我发过誓要保护它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I took an oath to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:00.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,保护什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Protect what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:02.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,古代奥义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The ancient wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:04.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我能理解你对此持怀疑态度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I understand your skepticism...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:06.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  你还真是心胸宽广\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you? How generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:07.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,可这里面还有别的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there are other things at play here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:10.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这些故事  它们仅仅是故事而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know these stories. And that is all that they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:12.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,比如共济会金字塔的神话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take the myth of the Masonic pyramid,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:15.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,建得如此之高  上帝都能一伸手就摸到它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}built so high God could reach out and touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:17.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是在告诉我  这里说的就是这些吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you're telling me that's what they're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:20.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,也许那些故事被刻意夸大了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, perhaps those stories were deliberately exaggerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:21.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,为了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To what end?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:24.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,为了让你这样的学者继续认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So that academics like you would continue to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:25.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,它们不过是神话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they're a myth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,就不会有人去寻找它们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So no one would search for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:28.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,这只是块石头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a piece of rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:30.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是一幅地图\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:37.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:40.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们应该去楼上继续讨论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe we should continue this discussion upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:48.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,共济会中有个派别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a sect within the Masons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:51.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,规模很小  异常秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very small and very secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:55.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,利维坦社\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Leviathan Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:57.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们的目的是确保\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our purpose is to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:14:00.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,古代奥义继续得以隐藏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that the ancient wisdom stays hidden,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:03.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,直到世界做好准备的那一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until such time as the world is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:04.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是彼得所希望的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is what Peter wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:07.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么他...他也宣誓加入你们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So h-he also took your oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:10.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,你说金字塔是幅地图  那是什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said the pyramid was a map. What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:13.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,据说把金字塔和尖顶石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is said that, when brought together,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:15.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,放到一起时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the pyramid and the capstone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:18.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,它们会揭示出入口的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}will reveal the location of the portal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:22.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得彼得会宁死来保护这个秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you think Peter would die to keep this secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:29.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有权坚守你的信仰  无论有多荒唐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're entitled to your beliefs, as unhinged as they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:31.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,但事关他的性命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but this is his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:44.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,说起来  这个秘密奥义是什么啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it, anyway, this secret wisdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:46.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,是个...公式吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it an... an equation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:47.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,一种祈祷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An invocation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:49.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,没人知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:51.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,至少活着的没人知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one living, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:56.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,这非常像爸爸的风格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, this is all very on-brand for Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:03.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,他总是说现代物理学\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He'd always say that modern physics
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:04.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,仅仅是开始理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was only starting to comprehend
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:06.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,古人们早已知道真实存在的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what the ancients knew to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:11.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,他是我从事这个工作的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's why I do what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:14.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,他对你的工作非常骄傲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's very proud of your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.92,0:15:18.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,通灵能力的起源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The genetics of psychic ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:20.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,集体意识...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}collective consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:25.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,很多人认为这是疯话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A lot of people think it's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:29.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,但虽说我很确信我是正确的  他们是错的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But for all my certainty that I'm right and they're wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:32.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的意识里总有这么个微小的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there is always a subtle voice in my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.44,0:15:34.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,有个疑虑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this doubt:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:36.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果这不是真的呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if it's not real?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:43.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,难道你不想知道这是不是真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't you want to know if it's real?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:47.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不清楚我该不该知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not sure I'm meant to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:51.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,我看到你看那个金字塔的神情了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw the way you looked at that pyramid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:53.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,我了解那种神情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know that look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.38,0:15:57.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,你可能再也不会有这种机会了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You may never get this chance again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:01.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,帮助我们找到它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help us find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:08.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,希伯来文...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Hebrew...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:14.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,是密码\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's code.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:18.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果真的是  那一定有办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If that's true, then there has to be a way
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:20.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,去破解它  一个密钥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to decipher it. A key.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.23,0:16:21.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:23.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,只有彼得有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Peter's the only one that has it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.47,0:16:25.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,过程就是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:26.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,一层面纱被揭开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One veil is lifted
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:28.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,露出来的不过是另一层面纱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}only to reveal another.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:30.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定会放在身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He'd have it close.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:32.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,放到他能看到的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Somewhere he can keep an eye on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:33.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,甚至也许就在他身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe even on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:38.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,我实验室保险柜的应急钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Override key for the safe in my lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.50,0:16:39.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,我时刻都戴着它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I keep it on me at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:43.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,-彼得戴什么首饰吗  -就一件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Does Peter even wear jewelry? - Just one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:44.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,他的戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:46.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不戴你的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't wear yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:47.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,只有在举行仪式时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only for functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:50.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,-很多共济会员都这样  -我爸爸不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- A lot of Masons do that. - Not my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:51.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,他总是戴着它  总是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He always wears his. Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:54.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,戒指很小  但并不意味着它没有隐藏着什么信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's small. It doesn't mean it's not concealing information.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:55.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,问题是  它现在被放在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Problem is: it's in the possession
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:56.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,国会警察那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of the Capitol Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:58.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想这些地道不可能让我们潜入\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't suppose these tunnels could sneak us
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:16:59.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,偷偷进入他们的证物房\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}into their evidence room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:01.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,这我就帮不了你们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't help you with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:03.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,也许我知道有人可以帮我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I might know someone who can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:07.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这是用猪骨头做的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know they make it out of pig bones, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:08.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,明胶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gelatin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:09.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是完全素食主义者吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You a vegan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:12.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,当然不是  我吃肉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hell no. I eat animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:15.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是只吃肉  其他部分不吃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The meat parts, not the... other parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:17.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,我可以给你拿点苹果酱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could... get you some applesauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:19.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,为什么全都是婴儿食品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why all the baby food?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:21.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,医生说子弹没打中任何重要部位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doctor said the bullet didn't hit anything important.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:24.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,但严格来说你还在手术恢复期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Still, you're technically recovering from surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:26.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  来点苹果酱吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, I'll take the applesauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:39.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,这么快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:41.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:43.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,你醒了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You awake, awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:44.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,你醒了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:53.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,应该醒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:56.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,有人来看你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:05.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,你感觉怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:08.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pretty good, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:10.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,医生说我一两天就可以出院了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doc says I could be out in a day or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:12.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的探员怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's your agent?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.58,0:18:13.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,燕麦奶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oat Milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:14.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,他没活下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:19.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,该死  抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Damn. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:21.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能告诉我他说了什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you tell me what he said?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:23.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,枪手  兰登的枪手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The shooter. To Langdon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:25.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:28.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,一切都很...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all just...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:32.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,没事  不必勉强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's okay. Don't force it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:35.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,他是什么人  那个清洁工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is he? The janitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,肯定有一些...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, there's got to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:40.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,监控录像  面部识别  指纹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}video, facial recognition, fingerprints...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:41.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,你查到他的身份了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You get an ID yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:43.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,不能说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.17,0:18:46.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,是我  记得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, it's me, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:48.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,阻止巨墙把我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The guy who stopped the giant wall
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:50.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,全都变成三明治的那个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from turning us all into panini?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:55.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,那个人来我的大楼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dude came into my building.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:18:59.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,那栋大楼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That building.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:02.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我的意思吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:07.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,把名字告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:13.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:15.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是个知其所需的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a need-to-know world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:22.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,好好休息吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:32.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\frz332\fs10\b0\3a&HFF\c&H7B8868\pos(162.4,163.2)}把手机扔了  他们可以追踪你们\N越过行者去找狼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.89,0:19:33.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,有人在帮他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone's helping them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:36.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我还是不知道他们是怎么离开那里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I still don't know how they got out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:37.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们搜查了车站的四面八方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We swept the station in every direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.83,0:19:40.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,-下面呢  -隧道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What about down? - The tunnels?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:42.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有公众能进入的入口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's no public access.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:44.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,这不是一个普通的公众\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This isn't a public person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:48.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想他们可能掉了这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think they might've dropped this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:53.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在凯瑟琳父亲房子里发现她的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you found Katherine in her father's house,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:55.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,你搜她身了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}did you search her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:19:58.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:01.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,25街的国会发电厂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Capitol Power Plant on 25th
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:03.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,应该能告诉我们谁能进入那些隧道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}should be able to tell us who has access to the tunnels.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:04.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,我现在就赶过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll head over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:05.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where you gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:06.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,彼得·所罗门家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Peter Solomon's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.73,0:20:40.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs12\frz11\b0\3a&HFF\c&H382206\pos(135.2,208)}格兰特·西蒙斯\N中情局特别探员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:43.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,干得好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:47.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要更多的镇静剂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll be needing more sedative.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:50.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,我去找我在医院的联络人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll go see my contact at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:53.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,除非你要我看着所罗门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unless you need me looking after Solomon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:55.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,不用  没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:57.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,他跑不掉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He isn't going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:54.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs12\frz359\b0\3a&HFF\c&H4C594C\t(0,3800,1,\t14)\move(266,251.2,272.4,245.867)}信仰联合医疗中心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.40,0:21:53.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:53.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,是政治原因吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was it political?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.96,0:21:55.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,他是暴动者还是什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was he some kind of insurrectionist, or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:21:58.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,不知道  他们正在想办法查清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know. They're trying to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.95,0:22:00.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,四年了  我睡觉的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, for four years I went to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.79,0:22:03.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,都害怕你会被爆炸装置炸飞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}afraid that you were gonna be blown up by an IED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:04.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,或是头被人砍掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or get your head chopped off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:06.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这里本应很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're supposed to be safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.42,0:22:08.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:10.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,我现在很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.81,0:22:11.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  打扰一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.90,0:22:14.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我要送他去做计算机断层扫描  -为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I need to borrow him for a CAT scan. - For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:16.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要更多伽马射线来扭曲我的DNA\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't need any more gamma rays warping my DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.42,0:22:18.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,我又不想成为蜘蛛侠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not trying to be Spider-Man over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.36,0:22:19.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,是绿巨人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Hulk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.70,0:22:22.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,伽马射线造出的是绿巨人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gamma rays created the Hulk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.22,0:22:24.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.36,0:22:25.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,我过会再来看你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.68,0:22:27.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.06,0:22:34.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,安吉拉在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's Angela?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.53,0:22:35.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是平常的那位护士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The usual nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.74,0:22:37.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,她生病回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Went home sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.81,0:22:41.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  先生  这位病人传染性极强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry, sir, this patient's extremely contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.34,0:22:42.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,说什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Say what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.10,0:22:47.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,我中枪了  没有传染性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got shot. I'm not infectious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:22:48.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们大概找错病人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe you got the wrong patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:50.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要你帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:22:53.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, hell no.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:31.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,我进去看看就出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just gonna take a quick look.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.85,0:23:34.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,中情局  你们今天可真忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}CIA. Busy day for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:35.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,你朋友刚走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your friend just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.88,0:24:08.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想我知道凯瑟琳是从哪拿到那封信了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think I know where Katherine got that envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.97,0:24:10.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,-信很重要吗  -不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Is it important? - No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.05,0:24:12.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道布莱克今天派其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know if Blake sent anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.18,0:24:14.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,-去所罗门家了吗  -据我所知没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- over to Solomon's house today? - Not that I know of.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.72,0:24:16.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,你认为他派人跟踪你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think he's got someone shadowing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.48,0:24:17.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,我并不觉得意外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wouldn't put it past him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.44,0:24:19.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在发电厂里找到了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What'd you find at the plant?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.90,0:24:22.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,发电厂为国会大厦和其他22座建筑供电\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So it services the Capitol and 22 other buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.82,0:24:24.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,其下有八千米的隧道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's five miles of tunnel down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.36,0:24:25.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.90,0:24:27.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们知道谁有权进去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}do we know who has access?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.99,0:24:29.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,工程师  技术服务人员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Engineers, service techs,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.66,0:24:31.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,三四名联邦特工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and three or four federal agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.12,0:24:35.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,国会大厦的建筑师也能进去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is the Architect of the Capitol one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.16,0:24:38.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,他的名字叫做沃伦·贝拉米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His name's Warren Bellamy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.42,0:24:42.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\frz0.9\fs10\b0\3a&HFF\c&H222726\pos(190.8,191.467)}沃伦·贝拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.13,0:24:43.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.21,0:24:45.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How'd you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.46,0:24:46.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我他的电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get me his phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.59,0:24:47.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,以及所有信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.41,0:25:12.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.53,0:25:13.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们正找你  伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're looking for you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.78,0:25:15.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果有其他选择  我们也不会来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We wouldn't be here if we had any other options.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.87,0:25:17.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,"我们"指的是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who's "we," anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.79,0:25:19.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是凯瑟琳·所罗门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm Katherine Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.29,0:25:20.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,彼得的女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Peter's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.08,0:25:22.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.46,0:25:23.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲的事我很遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And-and I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.92,0:25:26.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,-谢谢  -我们的时间不多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thanks. - We don't have a lot of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.09,0:25:28.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你们需要我做什么  -我们需要那个戒指\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What do you need from me? - We need the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.42,0:25:29.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,他手上戴的那个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.38,0:25:31.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,那个戒指是物证  在市中心一个储物柜里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The ring. That's evidence. It's in a locker downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.59,0:25:33.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能给谁打电话  把戒指拿出来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could you call someone? Ask to get it released?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.64,0:25:36.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,可以  就像外卖  也许来点蛋卷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sure, yeah, like takeout. Maybe get some egg rolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.26,0:25:38.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,你得派人进去签字领取\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'd have to have someone go in and sign it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.77,0:25:40.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有戒指我们只能凑合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll have to make do without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.89,0:25:42.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有其他选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we don't have any other options.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.86,0:25:46.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们到底要戒指干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you need it for, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.57,0:25:49.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,有一页记录着《旧约》中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's this page from the Old Testament,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.69,0:25:50.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,所罗门王故事的纸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the story of Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.82,0:25:53.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们认为它被编码过  那枚戒指可能包含\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We think it's encoded and that the ring could contain
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.36,0:25:55.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,某种解密秘钥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}some type of decryption key...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.20,0:25:56.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,行  好的  就说到这吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, okay, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.83,0:25:58.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,他会继续说下去  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He goes on, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.91,0:25:59.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,听着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.95,0:26:01.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,佐藤之前来看过我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sato came to see me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.91,0:26:02.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you were right,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.87,0:26:04.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,她有什么事瞒着我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there's something she's hiding from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.00,0:26:06.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,我能在处理一些秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can deal with secrets to a point,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.38,0:26:08.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,但当那家伙开枪后  我就受不了了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I passed that point when that guy started shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.34,0:26:13.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.43,0:26:16.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们得去趟洗衣店\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll need to head by the cleaners.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.01,0:26:18.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在那里还有一套制服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got another uniform there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.10,0:26:23.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,车不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nice ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.77,0:26:25.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,是我朋友的车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It belongs to a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.19,0:26:26.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  他是干什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah? What's he do?
