Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.94,0:26:46.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs12\frz5\b0\3a&HFF\c&H4C5637\t(0,1880,0.2,\move(378.8,249.067,415,249.067))}信仰联合医疗中心
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.77,0:27:08.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,不管那么多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here goes nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.48,0:27:10.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,我要是二十分钟没出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I'm not out in 20 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.02,0:27:12.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们就报警\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}call the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.54,0:27:29.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,你打算怎么跟你妈妈说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you going to tell your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.54,0:27:31.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么也不说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.63,0:27:34.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,她好不容易情绪稳定了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's finally in a relatively stable place,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.67,0:27:35.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.68,0:27:39.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不能把这些告诉她  现在不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't tell her about this. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.76,0:27:42.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,我应该去实验室签到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should check in at the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.47,0:27:46.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的手机还在小费盒里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And my phone is in a tip jar.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.06,0:27:49.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,假装现在是七十年代\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just pretend it's the '70s.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.90,0:27:51.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,-前蜂窝时代  -就不能是八十年代吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Pre-cellular. - Can it be the '80s?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.90,0:27:51.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}前蜂窝  第一代蜂窝电话的前身
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.82,0:27:52.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,八十年代...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The '80s...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.90,0:27:54.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,对  那些绝妙的音乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Great music.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.07,0:27:55.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,从各种文化角度来看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By every cultural measure,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.40,0:27:57.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,七十年代才是更好的十年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the '70s was the better decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.03,0:27:57.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,光是电影...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The films alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.95,0:27:59.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么  八十年代也有精彩的电影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? The '80s had amazing movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.95,0:28:01.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,《外星人》  《回到未来》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"E.T.," "Back to the Future,"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.66,0:28:02.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,-《威洛》...  -的确\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- "Willow"... - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.28,0:28:03.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我说的是一些成熟的电影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm talking about grown-up films.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.79,0:28:06.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,《教父》  《电视台风云》  《唐人街》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Godfather," "Network," "Chinatown"...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.16,0:28:07.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,《掠夺者》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Raiders."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.08,0:28:12.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,《掠夺者》  《掠夺者》  好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Raiders." "Raiders," okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.75,0:28:15.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们也有过愉快的几个月  不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We had a few good months, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.63,0:28:18.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,直到我的家庭爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Before my family exploded
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.88,0:28:20.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,并把所有人都卷入了危机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we got caught in the blast radius?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.89,0:28:22.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,十个半月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ten and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.85,0:28:24.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有很多事情要做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You had a lot going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.31,0:28:34.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,我爸跟你说过那件事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does Dad ever talk to you about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.15,0:28:39.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,关于扎克吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About Zack?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.03,0:28:43.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有  和你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. You?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.58,0:28:44.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.87,0:28:46.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉他认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel like he thinks
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.70,0:28:48.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会为所发生的事责怪他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I blame him for what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.63,0:28:53.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,这很艰难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, it's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.59,0:28:57.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道还有这些事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't know that was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.09,0:28:57.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,真遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.55,0:29:02.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想见见他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just want to see him,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.39,0:29:04.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他那不是他的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I can tell him it wasn't his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.27,0:29:09.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,一想到我可能没有机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The thought that I might not get the chance
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.77,0:29:11.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他这一点...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to tell him that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.60,0:29:12.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Katherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.36,0:29:16.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,你会有机会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're gonna get the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.44,0:29:17.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.74,0:29:21.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只是需要他知道我爱他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just need him to know that I love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.28,0:29:27.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,他不能像扎克那样结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It can't end with him the way it did with Zach.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.97,0:30:30.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,特别的凯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Special K.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.22,0:30:33.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,看起来真有教养\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looking very civilized.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.64,0:30:35.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,我真惊讶他们居然让你进来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm surprised they even let you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.15,0:30:37.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特认识的一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Robert knew someone
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.44,0:30:40.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,帮我走了走后门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who, uh, helped me pull some strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.57,0:30:44.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,你还和那个傻瓜在一起吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're still with that twat?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.62,0:30:48.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的脚怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened to your feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.29,0:30:53.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I was having
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.33,0:30:56.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,遇到了一些人际关系问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}some interpersonal issues in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.58,0:31:00.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,有谣言说我可能会试图逃跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and there was a rumor I might try to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.63,0:31:03.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以警卫们要确保我跑不了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So the guards made sure I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.13,0:31:05.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们不能这么对你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They can't do this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.38,0:31:06.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.80,0:31:07.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为人权吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Human rights?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.64,0:31:10.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,你来错地方了  凯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're in the wrong part of town, K.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.01,0:31:11.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们得把你弄出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have to get you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.97,0:31:13.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我们吗  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.14,0:31:15.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有过机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You had your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.15,0:31:22.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,爸本可以一个电话就把我救出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dad could have gotten me out with one phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.03,0:31:26.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我只收到了一封信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Instead, I got a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.16,0:31:31.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,"我不会允许你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"I won't allow you to play victim
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.58,0:31:35.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,在自己一手造成的情况下扮演受害者"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to circumstances you alone created."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.92,0:31:39.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,你听到了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you hear about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.92,0:31:42.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,我说这些干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.59,0:31:44.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,说不定还是你帮忙写的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You probably helped write it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.42,0:31:45.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  我反对他的做法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I didn't agree with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.88,0:31:48.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,你反对了啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, you disagreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.51,0:31:51.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,胆真大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How bold.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.85,0:31:55.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,我敢说  你立场一定很坚定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really stood your ground, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.86,0:32:03.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,很高心你能来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm glad you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.90,0:32:07.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,你可以帮我带个口信给他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can give him a message for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.16,0:32:19.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不再是他的儿子了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not his son anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.15,0:32:42.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,是这个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.61,0:32:44.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.03,0:32:48.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,好极了  我现在需要躺下了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Great. I'm-a go lie down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.42,0:33:32.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs12\b0\3a&HFF\c&H193031\pos(193,223.467)}扎克里·所罗门\N1987年生  2018年卒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.15,0:34:54.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.20,0:34:56.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,《希伯来圣经》  1814年发行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hebrew Bible. Published 1814.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.70,0:34:59.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,有三个部分  第一部分是《妥拉经》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's in three parts. The first part is the Torah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.24,0:35:03.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,两千年来  这三十万字只字未改\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}300,000 letters unchanged in over 2,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.41,0:35:06.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,犹太人保存经文的传统毋庸置疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Jewish tradition of preserving text is uncompromising.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.96,0:35:11.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果抄写员被发现增加  删减\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If a scribe is found to have added, subtracted
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.05,0:35:12.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,或修改了一个字母\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or altered a letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.59,0:35:15.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,整篇手稿都将作废并被掩埋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the whole manuscript is invalidated and buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.30,0:35:18.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.85,0:35:26.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.85,0:35:29.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,这一整段  希伯来语变了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This entire section-- the Hebrew has been changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.06,0:35:30.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,那意味着  这页是假的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what, the page is fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.15,0:35:33.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  被篡改了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, doctored.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.19,0:35:35.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,用来隐藏信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To hide a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.37,0:35:40.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,仔细看这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at it closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.37,0:35:42.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能看出有什么问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you see anything unusual about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.54,0:35:45.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,看起来没什么问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, looks normal enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.66,0:35:47.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,所有必备的标记都有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All the requisite markings are here:
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.21,0:35:50.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,双头鹰  三角形...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the double-headed eagle, triangle, the...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.04,0:35:52.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.71,0:35:54.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里应该是י\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is supposed to be a yod,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.88,0:35:56.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,但这是ה\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it's a he.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.38,0:35:57.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.97,0:36:01.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,这里的标记  珠宝商的失误吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, this mark on it. A jeweler's mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.02,0:36:08.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这看上去像什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What does that look like to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.73,0:36:12.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,π\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pi.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.03,0:36:17.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,那可不是错误  而是索引\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is not a mistake, it's a cipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.70,0:36:24.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,派\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pi.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.62,0:36:28.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,3.1415926...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}3.1415926...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.41,0:36:29.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,你背了圆周率\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You memorized pi?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.38,0:36:31.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.42,0:36:32.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,大学期间参加过一次比赛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did a competition in college once.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.88,0:36:35.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,背到了第417位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got to the 417th character.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.76,0:36:37.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,只背了417位吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only 417?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.76,0:36:38.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,我当时饿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got hungry.
